    .pd-card { background: #1f2937 !important; }
  }
  [data-ogsc] .pd-bg { background: #111827 !important; color: #f9fafb !important; }
  [data-ogsc] .pd-card { background: #1f2937 !important; }
</style></head><body class="pd-bg" style="background:#f9fafb"><table border="0" width="100%" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" align="center"><tbody><tr><td style="background:#f9fafb;color:#111827;margin:0;padding:0;font-family:-apple-system,&#x27;SF Pro Text&#x27;,system-ui,sans-serif"><table role="presentation" align="center" width="600" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" border="0" style="width:600px;max-width:100%;margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:100%;width:600px;background:#ffffff;padding:24px"><tbody><tr style="width:100%"><td><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;font-weight:bold;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Database failover detected</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" class="pd-card" style="border-left:4px solid #b91c1c;background-color:#fef2f2;padding:16px;margin:12px 0"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;color:#b91c1c;font-weight:bold;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Active incident</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Primary DB became unreachable at 14:32 UTC. Failover succeeded at 14:33.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">The primary database stopped responding to health checks at 14:32 UTC. The replica was promoted automatically and the API resumed serving traffic at 14:33 UTC. Investigate root cause before failing back.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">1. </p></td><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Confirm the replica is healthy and accepting writes.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">2. </p></td><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Page the on-call DBA to inspect the former primary.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody style="width:100%"><tr style="width:100%"><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">3. </p></td><td data-id="__react-email-column" style="vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Postpone non-critical migrations until failback is complete.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0"><code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:2px 6px;font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace;font-size:0.95em">$ kubectl rollout status deploy/api</code></p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0"><code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:2px 6px;font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace;font-size:0.95em">$ pgcli -h db-replica.svc -c &quot;SELECT 1&quot;</code></p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0"><code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:2px 6px;font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace;font-size:0.95em">$ tail -f /var/log/incident.log</code></p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0"><code style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:2px 6px;font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,monospace;font-size:0.95em">$ curl -s https://status.example.com/health</code></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding:8px 0"><tbody><tr><td><span><a href="https://status.example.com/incidents/2026-05-08" style="display:inline-block;border:2px solid #4f46e5;color:#4f46e5;padding:12px 22px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;border-radius:0">View incident dashboard</a></span></td></tr></tbody></table><img alt="DB CPU graph showing failover spike" src="https://example.com/img/db-cpu.png" style="display:block;outline:none;border:none;text-decoration:none;max-width:100%;height:auto"/><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;margin:12px 0"><tbody><tr><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Metric</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Threshold</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Actual</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Primary CPU</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">80%</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">99%</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">Replica lag</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">5s</p></td><td style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:8px 12px;vertical-align:top"><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-left:0">0.4s</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html><!--/$-->"
`;

